    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hope feels like a lie at this point. every time i think i might feel better, i just remember that he's gone and the world feels just as dark as it did yesterday. it's like i'm just waiting for something that's never coming back. it's exhausting to keep trying to find a reason to wake up every morning when everything just feels so hollow.",
